These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, pear, onion, lemon
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, malaysian, french, brazilian
1. the malaysian is on the left of the japanese##1
2. the person eating lettuce is the brazilian##1
3. the french is on the right of the japanese##1
4. the person eating pear is on the left of the brazilian##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lemon | onion | pear | lettuce   |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | japanese     | french   | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, baking, writing, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, golf, skateboarding, biathlon
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | writing | puzzles | baking | reading    |
| Sport   | skateboarding    | golf      | cricket | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, filmmaking, photography, drawing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, fantasy, zombie, martial-arts
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | gardening | drawing | photography   | filmmaking |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | zombie | martial-arts | fantasy         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, family, satire, romance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, snowboarding, handball
1. the person who's sport is golf is the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | family | spy  | satire      |
| Sport         | golf | handball   | snowboarding | biathlon |

