.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, mango, artichoke, plum
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, ferret, frog
1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
3. the person eating plum is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | plum | artichoke | mango | eggplant |
| Pet    | bird       | frog | ferret | cat     |

