.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, australian, canadian, turkish
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, snake, rat, hedgehog
1. the australian is on the far right##1
2. the turkish is on the left of the canadian##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the canadian##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian | malaysian | australian |
| Pet           | guinea-pig      | rat | hedgehog | snake    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, trance, punk, hip-hop
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
3. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
5. the fan of trance is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | punk | trance | rock | hip-hop  |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | goat | hedgehog       | goldfish |

