.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, social-worker, paramedic, security-guard
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, train, ship, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the social-worker##1
2. the person driving the roller is the security-guard##1
3. the social-worker is on the right of the engineer##1
4. the paramedic is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | paramedic | engineer      | social-worker | security-guard |
| Transport   | snowmobile          | train | ship     | roller    |

