.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, musical, martial-arts, disaster
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, subway, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical    | martial-arts       | time-travel | disaster   |
| Transport     | snowmobile | subway | skateboard   | boat |

