2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | soy-milk | fanta  | iced-tea | tea |
