.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, thai, japanese, brazilian
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, train, subway, trike
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the thai##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the chinese is on the left of the japanese##1
4. the brazilian is the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | chinese | japanese | thai | brazilian   |
| Transport     | subway  | skateboard    | train       | trike |

 